title: Photodisintegration of quasi-alpha-particles in nuclei Li-6,7 by gamma-ray with E(gamma)=35-55 MeV.

x4freetext: Results of experimental investigation of the reactions
Li-6,7(gamma,A+B)x with emission of charged particles
A and B, detected in coincidence are presented.
